A cyberpunk cityscape at night where holographic digital avatars of diverse people emerge from glowing screens and monitors, stepping onto rain-slicked neon-lit streets to gather in small groups at a futuristic café. The scene shows the merging of virtual and physical realms—translucent blue figures becoming increasingly solid and human as they move away from their screens. Towering skyscrapers covered in animated advertisements loom overhead, reflecting in puddles below. Steam rises from street vents, mixing with the pink and cyan glow of neon signs. In the foreground, a group of these transitioning figures huddle together around a small table, some still flickering with digital artifacts while others appear fully corporeal, engaged in animated conversation. The mood is simultaneously dystopian and hopeful—technology bringing isolated individuals into genuine human connection.
